text: Ksenia Kravchenko (born 5 February 1991) is a Russian volleyball player. She played at the 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix and 2015 Montreux Volley Masters. She played for VC Voronezh and Severyanka Cherepovets. == References == Category:1991 births Category:Russian volleyball players Category:Living people
